FBIS4-14416 "drsov062_a_94019" FBIS-SOV-94-062 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Chernomyrdin Arrives in Budapest Chernomyrdin Arrives in Budapest LD3103073394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0722 GMT 31 Mar 94 LD3103073394 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Budapest March 31 TASS -- Russian Premier Viktor Chernomyrdin arrived in Hungary on an official visit on Thursday. At the Budapest Airport, the Russian premier was welcomed by Hungarian Foreign Ministry Secretary of State Andras Kelemen, Hungarian Ambassador to Russia Gyergy Nanovscki, Russian Ambassador to Hungary Ivan Aboymov and other officials. Chernomyrdin and members of his delegation headed from the airport for the parliament building where there will be a welcoming ceremony for the Russian high guest.
